      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Is Simone Giertz a celebrity?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How about Aaron Franklin? Or Amanda Palmer? Or Jason Fried?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What about Josh Hanagarne or Luise Vindahl or Kai Brach?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If you know who they are, you would know they ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "are",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " in their own right.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Maybe not world-renown, but widely-known, at least in the small communities they occupy.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The thing is, I doubt any of these celebrities spend any amount of time concerned with what Selena Gomez is doing today.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "No. They got there by building a tribe.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "By consistently showing up. By caring enough to continue to create and share their art. By building a body of work as much as a body of loyal fans and followers.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You don’t reach stardom by people watching. You get there by reaching for it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}